5. Ask to commit
   └─ "Commit? (yes/no)"
```

## 🛠 Tech Stack

- **Expo SDK 52+**
- **React Native 0.76+** (New Architecture)
- **React 18.3+**
- **TypeScript 5.3+**
- **Test**: `npm test` (Jest)
- **Lint**: `npx expo lint`

## 📚 MCP Tools (Docs-First)

Available via `expo-workflow.skill`:
- `fetch_expo_sdk(module)` - expo-camera, expo-image, expo-video
