## Summary

This skill:
- ✅ Creates `.claude/` structure with principles
- ✅ Supports 6 variants: Generic, Nette, Flutter, Frontend, Expo, FastAPI
- ✅ Integrates with framework-specific workflow skills
- ✅ Enforces TDD, Git safety, Verification, Checkpoints
- ✅ Customizable Section 8 for project-specific rules
- ✅ **Optional:** Adds workflow-optimization (mistakes.md, verification.md, context pruning)

**Use:** "Setup this project" → Ready to develop!

## Integration with workflow-optimization

At the end of setup, user is offered workflow-optimization which adds:
- `mistakes.md` - Log errors with lessons learned (Cherny pattern)
- `verification.md` - Stack-specific pre-commit checklist
- CHECKPOINTS.md update - Auto-detect mistakes at session end
- [MAJOR]/[MINOR] tagging for ACTIVE_CONTEXT.md

This is optional but recommended for quality improvement.
